  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "A CONCURRENT RESOLUTION TO REQUEST THAT THE DEPARTMENT OF TRANSPORTATION NAME THE PORTION OF SOUTH MAIN STREET FROM THE GEORGIA PACIFIC FACILITY TO THE OLD NANTEX BUILDING AT CLAYTON STREET IN MCCORMICK COUNTY THE \"DR. BENJAMIN E. MAYS MEMORIAL HIGHWAY\" AND ERECT APPROPRIATE MARKERS OR SIGNS AT THIS LOCATION CONTAINING THE DESIGNATION."
    }
  ],
